Package org.cesecore.audit.enums

Enum Class EventTypes

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Enum<EventTypes>
org.cesecore.audit.enums.EventTypes
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparable<EventTypes>, Constable, org.cesecore.audit.enums.ConstantType<org.cesecore.audit.enums.EventType>, org.cesecore.audit.enums.EventType
public enum EventTypes extends Enum<EventTypes> implements org.cesecore.audit.enums.EventType
Contains all event types that CESeCore core needs to log to secure audit log. When doing secure audit log it is necessary to identify the event being logged.
